### Allergen Bitmask

| Bit | Value | Allergen |
|---|---|---|
| 0 | 1 | Celery |
| 1 | 2 | Cereals containing gluten |
| 2 | 4 | Crustaceans |
| 3 | 8 | Eggs |
| 4 | 16 | Fish |
| 5 | 32 | Lupin |
| 6 | 64 | Milk |
| 7 | 128 | Molluscs |
| 8 | 256 | Mustard |
| 9 | 512 | Tree nuts |
| 10 | 1024 | Peanuts |
| 11 | 2048 | Sesame |
| 12 | 4096 | Soybeans |
| 13 | 8192 | Sulphur dioxide / sulphites |

A dish's allergen profile = bitwise OR of all its ingredient allergen_flags.
A customer's safe dishes = WHERE (dish_allergens & customer_allergens) = 0.

