## Regulatory Context

- **Food Information Regulations 2014** — requires allergen information for non-prepacked food
- **FSA Best Practice Guidance (March 2025)** — sets expectation of written allergen information
- **Owen's Law** — proposed mandatory written allergen labelling, FSA evaluation from spring 2026
- **Natasha's Law (October 2021)** — mandatory ingredient labelling for PPDS food (adjacent)
- **UK GDPR Article 9** — special-category data requires explicit consent
- **PECR** — marketing communications require separate consent
- **ICO Special Category Guidance** — explicit opt-in, granular consent, deletion rights

